# Mutable counter

R.2.2 demo: a single `var` + reassignment + while loop.

```scalascript
@main def run(): Unit =
  var count: Long = 0
  while (count < 5) {
    count = count + 1
  }
  println(count)
```

Build and run:

```bash
ssc build-rust mutable-counter.ssc
./mutable-counter            # → 5
```
